text: Maayke Tjin-A-Lim also written as Maayke Tjin A-Lim (born 10 January 1998) is a Dutch track and field athlete who is specialized in the sprint hurdles events. She is medalist at the Dutch national indoor and outdoor championships. Tjin-A-Lim represents Netherlands at international competitions. In 2022 she competed at the 2022 World Athletics Indoor Championships in the 60 metres hurdles event and at the 2022 European Athletics Championships in the 100 metres hurdles event where she reached the semi-finals. ==References== Category:1998 births Category:Dutch hurdlers Category:Living people
